[GENTLE MUSIC]

02:41.987 --> 02:43.163
-HEY SUMMER!

02:44.425 --> 02:45.991
-HEY ETHAN.

02:46.122 --> 02:48.124
-ARE YOU COMING TO MY
PARTY WITH MATT OR SLADE?

02:48.255 --> 02:51.127
-MATT, SLADE'S STILL
SOMEWHERE IN BARBADOS.

02:51.258 --> 02:54.826
-WAS, MAYBE. I JUST SAW HIM
DOING 360 AIRS OFF SUNSET BEACH.

